						               													<description>&amp;quot;YOU CAN RUN BUT YOU CAN'T HIDE.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A twenty-foot square ring doesn&amp;rsquo;t give you much room to move and definitely nowhere to hide. Boxing - it&amp;rsquo;s called the &amp;ldquo;Sweet Science&amp;rdquo; for a reason. You can move around your opponent flicking jabs and dancing away. &amp;ldquo;Rope a dope&amp;rdquo; and pick your spots firing punches and scoring points. All that skillful stuff, putting on a boxing clinic and looking pretty while you&amp;rsquo;re doing it. Then.... BOOM!&amp;#10;Your opponent throws a hook from downtown and &amp;ldquo;out go the lights!&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Friday Night Fights is unlike any boxing game you've ever played. With FNF you can... Build your fighter the way you want him. Boxer or slugger it's all up to you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Fight your way to the title through 36 pre-generated fighters that are run by the game mechanics.&amp;#10;     Become a promoter with your own fighters. Train them and pick and choose your opponents on your way to the top.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Everything you need to start your own &amp;ldquo;fight club&amp;rdquo; with your friends is included. It&amp;rsquo;s an exciting game where you have to think as you fight. Do you go &amp;ldquo;all out&amp;rdquo; as soon as the bell rings? Or maybe pace yourself for the full fight? And what&amp;rsquo;s he doing?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you have the heart of a Champion? Only you can tell. Friday Night Fights &amp;ndash; &amp;ldquo;Play to win&amp;hellip;&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
